{
  "title": "Portfolio Observability Command Center",
  "uid": "portfolio-observability-cc",
  "schemaVersion": 39,
  "version": 1,
  "editable": true,
  "timezone": "browser",
  "refresh": "1m",
  "time": {
    "from": "now-24h",
    "to": "now"
  },
  "templating": {
    "list": [
      {
        "name": "project_name",
        "type": "query",
        "datasource": {
          "type": "loki",
          "uid": "grafana_lokiq"
        },
        "query": "label_values({log_type=\"http\"}, project_name)",
        "includeAll": true,
        "allValue": ".*",
        "multi": true,
        "current": {
          "selected": true,
          "text": "All",
          "value": [
            "$__all"
          ]
        }
      },
      {
        "name": "service_name",
        "type": "query",
        "datasource": {
          "type": "loki",
          "uid": "grafana_lokiq"
        },
        "query": "label_values({project_name=~\"${project_name:regex}\",log_type=\"http\"}, service_name)",
        "includeAll": true,
        "allValue": ".*",
        "multi": true,
        "current": {
          "selected": true,
          "text": "All",
          "value": [
            "$__all"
          ]
        }
      },
      {
        "name": "host",
        "type": "query",
        "datasource": {
          "type": "loki",
          "uid": "grafana_lokiq"
        },
        "query": "label_values({project_name=~\"${project_name:regex}\",service_name=~\"${service_name:regex}\",log_type=\"http\"}, host)",
        "includeAll": true,
        "allValue": ".*",
        "multi": true,
        "current": {
          "selected": true,
          "text": "All",
          "value": [
            "$__all"
          ]
        }
      },
      {
        "name": "prom_job",
        "type": "query",
        "datasource": {
          "type": "prometheus",
          "uid": "grafana_prometheus"
        },
        "query": "label_values(up, job)",
        "includeAll": true,
        "allValue": ".*",
        "multi": true,
        "current": {
          "selected": true,
          "text": "All",
          "value": [
            "$__all"
          ]
        }
      }
    ]
  },
  "panels": [
    {
      "id": 1,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Portfolio Request Rate by Project (req/s)",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "loki",
        "uid": "grafana_lokiq"
      },
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 0 },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sum by (project_name) (rate({project_name=~\"${project_name:regex}\",service_name=~\"${service_name:regex}\",host=~\"${host:regex}\",log_type=\"http\"} | logfmt [5m]))",
          "refId": "A",
          "legendFormat": "{{project_name}}"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Total Requests (selected range)",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "loki",
        "uid": "grafana_lokiq"
      },
      "gridPos": { "h": 4, "w": 4, "x": 12, "y": 0 },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sum(count_over_time({project_name=~\"${project_name:regex}\",service_name=~\"${service_name:regex}\",host=~\"${host:regex}\",log_type=\"http\"} | logfmt [$__range]))",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Suspicious Share",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "__expr__",
        "uid": "__expr__"
      },
      "gridPos": { "h": 4, "w": 4, "x": 16, "y": 0 },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "percentunit",
          "decimals": 2
        }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": {
            "type": "loki",
            "uid": "grafana_lokiq"
          },
          "expr": "sum(count_over_time({project_name=~\"${project_name:regex}\",service_name=~\"${service_name:regex}\",host=~\"${host:regex}\",log_type=\"http\"} | logfmt [$__range]))",
          "refId": "A"
        },
        {
          "datasource": {
            "type": "loki",
            "uid": "grafana_lokiq"
          },
          "expr": "sum(count_over_time({project_name=~\"${project_name:regex}\",service_name=~\"${service_name:regex}\",host=~\"${host:regex}\",log_type=\"http\"} | logfmt | status=~\"403|444\" [$__range]))",
          "refId": "B"
        },
        {
          "datasource": {
            "type": "__expr__",
            "uid": "__expr__"
          },
          "expression": "$B / ($A + 0.000001)",
          "type": "math",
          "refId": "C"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Bot-target Pressure (req/s)",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "loki",
        "uid": "grafana_lokiq"
      },
      "gridPos": { "h": 4, "w": 4, "x": 20, "y": 0 },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "(sum(rate({project_name=~\"${project_name:regex}\",service_name=~\"${service_name:regex}\",host=~\"${host:regex}\",log_type=\"http\"} | logfmt | traffic_class=\"suspicious\" | endpoint_class=\"bot_target\" [5m])) or sum(rate({project_name=~\"${project_name:regex}\",service_name=~\"${service_name:regex}\",host=~\"${host:regex}\",log_type=\"http\"} | logfmt | uri=~\"(?i)^/(\\\\.env|\\\\.git|\\\\.htaccess|wp-admin|wp-login|phpmyadmin|server-status|config\\\\.php|backup\\\\.sql).*\" [5m])))",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Suspicious Traffic Rate by Service (req/s)",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "loki",
        "uid": "grafana_lokiq"
      },
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 8 },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "(sum by (service_name) (rate({project_name=~\"${project_name:regex}\",service_name=~\"${service_name:regex}\",host=~\"${host:regex}\",log_type=\"http\"} | logfmt | traffic_class=\"suspicious\" [5m])) or sum by (service_name) (rate({project_name=~\"${project_name:regex}\",service_name=~\"${service_name:regex}\",host=~\"${host:regex}\",log_type=\"http\"} | logfmt | status=~\"403|444\" [5m])))",
          "refId": "A",
          "legendFormat": "{{service_name}}"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 6,
      "type": "table",
      "title": "Top Bot-target Endpoints",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "loki",
        "uid": "grafana_lokiq"
      },
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 6, "x": 12, "y": 8 },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "topk(20, sum by (uri) (count_over_time({project_name=~\"${project_name:regex}\",service_name=~\"${service_name:regex}\",host=~\"${host:regex}\",log_type=\"http\"} | logfmt | endpoint_class=\"bot_target\" [$__range])))",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "options": {
        "showHeader": true
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 7,
      "type": "table",
      "title": "Top Suspicious Sources",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "loki",
        "uid": "grafana_lokiq"
      },
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 6, "x": 18, "y": 8 },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "topk(20, sum by (remote_addr) (count_over_time({project_name=~\"${project_name:regex}\",service_name=~\"${service_name:regex}\",host=~\"${host:regex}\",log_type=\"http\"} | logfmt | traffic_class=\"suspicious\" [$__range])))",
          "refId": "A",
          "legendFormat": "{{remote_addr}}"
        },
        {
          "expr": "topk(20, sum by (srcIp) (count_over_time({project_name=~\"${project_name:regex}\",service_name=~\"${service_name:regex}\",host=~\"${host:regex}\",log_type=\"http\"} | logfmt | traffic_class=\"suspicious\" [$__range])))",
          "refId": "B",
          "legendFormat": "{{srcIp}}"
        }
      ],
      "options": {
        "showHeader": true
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 8,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Prometheus Target Availability by Job",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "grafana_prometheus"
      },
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 16 },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "avg by (job) (up{job=~\"${prom_job:regex}\"})",
          "refId": "A",
          "legendFormat": "{{job}}"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 9,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Global Scrape Health",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "grafana_prometheus"
      },
      "gridPos": { "h": 4, "w": 4, "x": 12, "y": 16 },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "percentunit",
          "decimals": 2
        }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "avg(up{job=~\"${prom_job:regex}\"})",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 10,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "HTTP 5xx Rate by Job (if exported)",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "grafana_prometheus"
      },
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 8, "x": 16, "y": 16 },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sum by (job) (rate(http_requests_total{job=~\"${prom_job:regex}\",status=~\"5..\"}[5m])) or vector(0)",
          "refId": "A",
          "legendFormat": "{{job}}"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 11,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "P95 Request Latency by Job (if exported)",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "grafana_prometheus"
      },
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 24 },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.95, sum by (le, job) (rate(http_request_duration_seconds_bucket{job=~\"${prom_job:regex}\"}[5m]))) or vector(0)",
          "refId": "A",
          "legendFormat": "{{job}}"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 12,
      "type": "traces",
      "title": "Recent Traces (Tempo)",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "tempo",
        "uid": "grafana_tempo"
      },
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 24 },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "queryType": "search",
          "query": "{}",
          "limit": 20
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 13,
      "type": "text",
      "title": "Operator Pivot Guide",
      "gridPos": { "h": 7, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 32 },
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "### Fast triage flow\\n1. **Traffic spike?** Start with `Portfolio Request Rate` and `Suspicious Share`.\\n2. **Security pressure?** Check `Bot-target Pressure`, `Top Bot-target Endpoints`, and `Top Suspicious Sources`.\\n3. **Reliability degradation?** Use `Target Availability`, `Global Scrape Health`, `5xx Rate`, and `P95 Latency`.\\n4. **Trace pivot:** Open Explore -> Tempo when a service has elevated error/latency and inspect recent traces.\\n\\nThis dashboard is designed for portfolio-level anomaly detection first, then service-level drill-down."
      }
    }
  ]
}
